    "body": "Actually, not sure what is missing here\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.0;\r\ncontract C {\r\n    function f() public pure {\r\n        address a = address(0);\r\n        bytes20 b = 0;\r\n        \r\n        b = bytes20(a);\r\n        a = address(b);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nCompiles fine.\r\n\r\nHowever, explicit conversion `address payable <=> bytes20` is not allowed though.\r\n\r\n",
